name: about:blank - Washout
description:
A subtle about:blank style which shows a very faded watermark of the Firefox logo. Gentle on the eyes, but stylish.

I was actually surprised no one did this yet.


CHANGELOG:  

1.0.1 - 
Original release.

1.1.0 -
FEATURE: Base64-encoded images are now used instead of hotlinked images from my server.
FIX: Added a background color declaration to override the default color of Firefox.
REMOVAL: The larger image is not available in this new version because of space constrains for the maximum character limit at userstyles.org.
css:
/*------------------------------------------------------------------------------
washout.css 
SHEET NAME:  Washout
BY:          Corey Csuhta 
Site:        http://cjcsuhta.com/projects/washout/
VERSION:     1.1.0
FUNCTION:    A subtle style for Firefox's about:blank page.

CHANGELOG:  1.0.1   Original release.
            1.1.0   FEATURE:    Base64-encoded images are now used instead of 
                                hotlinked images from my server.
                    FIX:        Added a background color declaration to override
                                the default color of Firefox.
                    REMOVAL:    The larger image is not available in this new version 
                                because of space constrains for the maximum character
                                limit at userstyles.org.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
@namespace url(http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml);
@-moz-document url("about:blank") {
    * {
        background: url("data:image/png;base64,") #FFF;

        margin: 0px;
        background-position: center;
        background-attachment: fixed;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;

    }
}
